data.description: This gorgeous villa is an end unit on a dead end street in beautiful Delray Villas, a 55+ adult community. This villa was recently remodeled and features new appliances! Enjoy your morning coffee from the comfort of your screened in porch! Very large living/dining room area and it also features a beautiful sun room! Master bedroom and guestroom boast an incredible water view! Hurricane impact windows throughout the entire hime! This is truly a gem! Come see this before it is gone!!
